<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>76</hymn_number>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw Bethlehem nang khua hmete, Dai tein na um ziar ko! Naa hngilh
 karah nangmah cungin, Dai tein arfi an lan. A daimi na lam cung ah,
 Zungzal ceunak a tlang, Kum tam ruahchannak le tihnak, Nangmah ah an i
 tong.

[V2]
 Maw nannih deirel arfi hna, Mithiang chuahnak kha chim u, Pathian
 thangthat in mi sinah, Daihnak um ko seh, ti in. Meri nih Khrih a hrin
 cang, Vancungmi an i pum, Mi hngilh lioah an rung tum i, Dawtnak in an
 rung zoh.

[V3]
 Dai te in khuaruahhar bikmi, Laksawng cu a kan pek cang; Pathian nih a
 van thluachuahnak, Vawlei mi kha a cheuh hna. Leicung mi nih a rat
 thawng, An thei kho lo nain, Lungnemmi vialte lung chungah, Bawi Khrih cu
 a lut lai.

[V4]
 A thiangmi Bethlehem Ngakchia, Kannih sinah rung tum tuah, Kan sualnak
 hlonh in kan chungah, Lut law nihin hring than tuah; Vanmi nih Khrismas
 lawmhnak, An chimmi thawng kan theih, Kan sin ra tuah, Kan sin um tuah,
 Kan Bawi Immanuel.</lyrics>
<title>MAW BETHLEHEM NANG KHUA HMETE CH76</title>
</song>